 British Council - Performers in Profile 2010 International about us t tour schedule shows press contact us Bash Street Theatre Company produce inventive and fast-moving comic-strip shows, featuring a fusion of live music, physical theatre and circus skills. Street shows, walkabouts and mid-scale productions are toured to indoor/outdoor venues and festivals throughout the UK, Europe and beyond. Bash Street Theatre Roz am Poullou 29690 Locmaria Berrien France UTE CLASSEN KULTURMANAGEMENT theaterstrae 15 52062 aachen germany www.ute-classen.de info@ute-classen.de | | 
